{
  "stem": "27335.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the reason that it never became a town was because it was too close-- only, only 16 kilometers from the provincial-- provincial capital, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it remained a big village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was a very, very advanced culture, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right-- right in that village--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, 1912-- how old you are?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "19-- December 12, 1912.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it is whenever I say it, they ask me, and so it-- it raise a smile right away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's a lot to remember, because I was-- I was two years old, already, when the war broke out, and my father was one of the very first one to be-- to be drafted.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, uh, like most of those through Hungary army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the way it worked, the most backward people- like the Bosnians-- were the very first, first one in the front line, in the storming line.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the second, there was the Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the third line were the Austrians-- that's how the Austro-Hungarian empire worked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, very vividly, the first time about the war in 1918, when we saw the first airplane-- a French plane flew over-- over Hungary and over our village.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was, as you can imagine by the, by geography.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was close to the-- to Bosnia, toward Russian front.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a lot of things is happened around there, a ton of troops, uh, going through there at the train line, leading through there, in my village.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so-- and I remembered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, only at the end, end of the war, where finally the Russians army were forcing the [NON-ENGLISH] back, and then again did a team as far as the province that you come from.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You name it, now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
